You can attach a few files for test decryption by packing them into an archive with zip, rar, tar, 7zip, 7z, tar.gz extensions of no more than 10 megabytes using the attach button directly in the chat.

If your archive weighs more than 10 megabytes, please use our file sharing service.

Please wait for a reply, sometimes it takes several hours due to possible time zone differences.

it's normal price for your company
but you can make your offer

Our company is doing so badly. I hope you can help us.
How do I know if you can help me get rid of the virus?
Sorry, i can't help you in this situation
Can you unlock the small file I gave you
i'll provide you decrypted file a little bit latter
Do you have different prices for different companies? Why are we so expensive
This is the minimum price for a company of your size; if the company were in another country the price would be 3-4 times higher
Thank you for your reply. We will discuss it internally
